                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160918-113-off589 t18160918-113-cd590"></join>, a watch, value 4l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18160918-113-victim863" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Richardson
                        <interp inst="t18160918-113-victim863" type="surname" value="Richardson"></interp>
